name: Garry Shark Attack Demo
description:
Gerry of the advance attack force for the Shark Empire has come across members of the rebel Sea Alliance, or more commonly known among the empire , Shiny Smelly Yum Yums. Defeat the rebels and blast your way through fish after fish after turtle and maybe one day a Jellyfish....but those things can hurt so maybe best avoid the Jellyfish unless you feeling Jelly?

Current version is still being developed, more players, enemies, boss, as well as pickups are being worked on and added. Thanks for playing and hope you enjoy, also please leave me any feedback you may have.
